Date: Mon, 18 May 1998 11:00:47 -0700
From: Eileen Lawrence <elawrenc@doh.gov.uk>

You posted a notice from Ralph Blanchfield on 6 May in which he kindly drew
attention to the revised guidance for laboratory and healthcare workers on
safe working with TSE agents.
You might wish to inform your readers that the full text of this guidance
is available on The Stationary Office website address:
<http://www.official-documents.co.uk>
--
